{
  "stem": "24163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was talking about my arrest by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, someone came from an upper level, or a different office.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I overheard, briefly, that-- words like, in German, like, we can't keep him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With that, the stormtrooper who had threatened me the most, who told me he was going to hang me by my testicles on the flagpole outside, and all what went on, with the-- with the things they threatened me with, you wouldn't believe, besides deportation.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, we're going to let you go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're going to give you two minutes to leave this building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if you're not out of here and out of sight within two minutes, we will shoot you for trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "With that, he opened the door, and those big steel doors, which they had at headquarters, the Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I ran down the steps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I see these steps in front of my eyes today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't walk those steps, I raced those steps down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I must have raced home like a gazelle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I walked into the house, my stepmother said, what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to her, I became ill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I did not tell her what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was so much on their minds and so much going on, I didn't want to burden them with my arrest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew, the most important thing, I had a signed document which was given to me at the social security office, which said that my social security had been paid.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had an-- a document from the [GERMAN], the tax office, that my taxes were paid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew, with these documents, I would get the visa, and I would leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
